{
  "project": "radishflow",
  "task": "suggest_flowsheet_edits",
  "status": "success",
  "confidence": 0.95,
  "summary": "基于当前诊断结果，针对未连接的气相产物流股（Separator Vapor 71）、缺失流率规定的进料流股（Charge Heater Feed）以及缺少压力参数的闪蒸罐（Hot Flash Separator）生成了3个候选编辑提案。",
  "answers": [
    "针对选中的对象和相关的诊断信息，已生成三个候选编辑建议：首先为未连接的闪蒸罐气相流股建议一个拓扑连接占位符；其次为加热器进料流股补充必需的流率规定占位符；最后为设置为固定压力模式的闪蒸罐补充操作压力参数占位符。"
  ],
  "issues": [
    {
      "description": "Separator Vapor 71 缺少下游连接或输出节点，导致拓扑不完整。",
      "severity": "error",
      "citations": [
        "diag-1",
        "flowdoc-stream-3",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "description": "Charge Heater Feed 缺失关键的流率规格设定。",
      "severity": "error",
      "citations": [
        "diag-2",
        "flowdoc-stream-1",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "description": "Hot Flash Separator 处于固定压力模式但缺失操作压力目标值参数。",
      "severity": "error",
      "citations": [
        "diag-3",
        "flowdoc-unit-2",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "requires_confirmation": true,
  "proposed_actions": [
    {
      "action": "candidate_edit",
      "title": "补充气相产物流股下游连接 (Separator Vapor 71)",
      "target": {
        "type": "stream",
        "id": "separator-vapor-71"
      },
      "rationale": "诊断报告指出该气相流股尚未连接到任何下游设备或接收器，这导致整体拓扑无效（invalid_topology）。需要指定一个合法的接收目标以完成拓扑连接。",
      "patch": {
        "connection_placeholder": {
          "target_unit_id": "<REQUIRED_DOWNSTREAM_OR_SINK>"
        }
      },
      "risk_level": "high",
      "requires_confirmation": true,
      "citations": [
        "diag-1",
        "flowdoc-stream-3",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "action": "candidate_edit",
      "title": "完善进料流股规格 (Charge Heater Feed)",
      "target": {
        "type": "stream",
        "id": "feed-71"
      },
      "rationale": "进料流股缺少流率设定，且下游状态依赖于此，需要提供并补充此流率规范以便求解器继续计算。",
      "patch": {
        "spec_placeholders": {
          "flow_rate": "<REQUIRED_FLOW_RATE>"
        }
      },
      "risk_level": "medium",
      "requires_confirmation": true,
      "citations": [
        "diag-2",
        "flowdoc-stream-1",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "action": "candidate_edit",
      "title": "配置闪蒸罐操作压力 (Hot Flash Separator)",
      "target": {
        "type": "unit",
        "id": "separator-7"
      },
      "rationale": "当前设备被设定为“固定压力模式（fixed）”，但缺少明确的操作压力设定值，这属于单元参数不完整。需要提供具体的压力目标。",
      "patch": {
        "parameter_placeholders": {
          "config": {
            "operating_pressure_kpa": "<REQUIRED_PRESSURE_TARGET>"
          }
        }
      },
      "risk_level": "medium",
      "requires_confirmation": true,
      "citations": [
        "diag-3",
        "flowdoc-unit-2",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
